name: C.B.C
body: ### Welcome to the official C.B.C homepage. ### What is C.B.C? The Command-Based-Calculator is a homebrew calculator for 3/2ds systems. ### Is it stable? I have not gotten around to importing/compiling the source code with the necessary libraries. So, no. It's an .exe file. ### Authors and Contributors AnonBeing/AnonEx(my aliases.)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
